# MuseDAM Figma Component Mapper (Auto Mapping Skill)

## Trigger Conditions
- Figma link provided + any component/layer name mentioned
- Reskin or new component generation

## Mandatory Workflow (execute before any code generation)
1. Extract Figma layer/component names (use 06 rules).
2. Check against existing project:
   - Exact match in src/components/ui/ (Button, Input, Card, Dialog, Table, etc.)
   - Exact match in root business components (AssetThumbnail, ConfirmDialog, UserAvatar, UserSelect, etc.)
   - Domain folders (approval-center/, dnd/, upload/, etc.)
3. Mapping Rules (priority order):
   - Figma "Button/Primary/Medium" → import { Button } from '@/components/ui/button'
   - Figma "Asset Card" or "IP Card" → reuse AssetThumbnail or create in domain folder
   - Figma "Table" → reuse or map to shadcn Table + our Table styles
   - Unknown → create in correct domain folder + add data-component comment
